description:
follow me on Instagram, Youtube, Patreon and my website.

Hedy Lamarr

Suggested Weight: 1.0

Suggested prompts

  • 1988 color horror movie poster of h3dy14m4rr

  • add "color" to the prompt (color photo, color poster, etc) otherwise it will likely be b&w

  • The hair style is somewhat baked in, to get straight hair you will need to strongly emphasize that in the prompt like ((straight hair))

Training

  • trained on ~23 images

  • Learning Rate: 0.005:1000, 0.001:2000, 0.0001:5000, 0.00005

  • Total Steps: 15,000

  • Batch Size: 1

  • Gradient Steps: 1
